txt.en:
'If you're hungry, you've come to the right place! But I hope you're VERY hungry, [placeholder]. This is the Eating Contest, and it's no laughing matter.

'There are five stations, and you must run to each of them. You get a small reward for completing the first few meals, and great rewards for completing the fifth meal before the three minutes are over and the event finishes.

'Are you ready? Just wait here for me to say when the event begins.'
'Well, I'd imagine you're fuller now than when you started! Now it's time for the second phase, though. I hope you have plenty of room left....'
The Biggest Stomach of Them All
Let the stuffing begin!
'The eating contest will begin shortly! I hope you left plenty of room if you plan to participate, [placeholder]. Wait here -- you'll be eating soon enough.'
